{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"takeRef","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV","text":"ObjectRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In other words, this function will convert a floating reference (if","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"present) into a full reference."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Typically you want to use ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_ref_sink()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in order to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"automatically do the correct thing with respect to floating or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"non-floating references, but there is one specific scenario where"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this function is helpful."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The situation where this function is helpful is when creating an API","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that allows the user to provide a callback function that returns a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"GObject. We certainly want to allow the user the flexibility to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"return a non-floating reference from this callback (for the case"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"where the object that is being returned already exists)."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"At the same time, the API style of some popular GObject-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"libraries (such as Gtk) make it likely that for newly-created GObject","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"instances, the user can be saved some typing if they are allowed to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"return a floating reference."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Using this function on the return value of the user’s callback allows"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the user to do whichever is more convenient for them. The caller will"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"always receives exactly one full reference to the value: either the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"one that was returned in the first place, or a floating reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that has been converted to a full reference."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function has an odd interaction when combined with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_ref_sink()"},{"text":" running at the same time in another thread on","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the same ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object"},{"type":"text","text":" instance. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_ref_sink()"},{"type":"text","text":" runs first then"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the result will be that the floating reference is converted to a hard","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reference. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_take_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" runs first then the result will be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that the floating reference is converted to a hard reference and an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"additional reference on top of that one is added. It is best to avoid"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"this situation.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/takeRef()"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is floating, sink it.  Otherwise, do nothing."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref\/takeref()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolPAAE7takeRefAA0bE0VSgyF::SYNTHESIZED::s:10GLibObject10BindingRefV","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GLibObject","title":"takeRef()","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"takeRef","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/ObjectRef":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/ObjectRef","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/objectref","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The base object type."}],"role":"symbol","title":"ObjectRef"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingRef/takeRef()":{"abstract":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is floating, sink it.  Otherwise, do nothing."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref\/takeref()","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"takeRef"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ObjectRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B3RefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"title":"takeRef()","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/takeRef()"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","abstract":[],"title":"GLibObject","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingRef":{"title":"BindingRef","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"BindingRef"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"BindingRef","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject"},{"text":" instance (or source) and another property on another ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instance (or target)."}]},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/BindingRef/ObjectProtocol-Implementations":{"title":"ObjectProtocol Implementations","abstract":[],"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/bindingref\/objectprotocol-implementations","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/BindingRef\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations","role":"collectionGroup"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object":{"title":"Object","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The base object type."}],"role":"symbol"}}}